Gagar (; ) is a rural locality (a selo) in Kolobsky Selsoviet, Tlyaratinsky District, Republic of Dagestan, Russia. Population:
Geography
Gagar is located 35&nbsp;km southeast of Tlyarata (the district's administrative centre) by road. Tsimguda is the nearest rural locality.
